		{"type":"text","text":"论文作者分布定律","id":"ae2e92ed3589d8fc","x":-1240,"y":2049,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"type":"text","text":"也称洛特卡定律。揭示论文作者的频率和论文篇数之间的关系：$f(x)=C/x^a$","id":"6b9cdd1d51540ef1","x":-2057,"y":2034,"width":461,"height":91},
		{"type":"text","text":"引文","id":"376530bd08f3b935","x":-1240,"y":2482,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"type":"text","text":"期刊影响因子","id":"3306f610134d9e57","x":-1240,"y":2938,"width":250,"height":60},
